Other public general laws that may affect land use in a local jurisdiction under this division, Division II of this article, or otherwise, include:
Article 23A, §§ 2(30) and (36), 9, 19, and 19A(e) of the Code;
Article 25, § 3 of the Code;
Article 25A, § 5 of the Code;
Article 25B, § 13 of the Code; and
Title 8, Subtitle 18 of the Natural Resources Article.
